We want to be able to view session recordings of how users interact with our platform so that we can improve ease of use and conversion throughout the process.

To do this we need to copy and paste the script below into the <head> of every page:

{noformat}<script>
window['_fs_debug'] = false;
window['_fs_host'] = 'fullstory.com';
window['_fs_script'] = 'edge.fullstory.com/s/fs.js';
