</script>{noformat}



We would also like to capture the following data with each session recording: [https://help.fullstory.com/hc/en-us/articles/360020623294-FS-setUserVars-Recording-custom-user-data|https://help.fullstory.com/hc/en-us/articles/360020623294-FS-setUserVars-Recording-custom-user-data|smart-link] 

* User:
** ID
** Email
** Name
* Company:
** ID
** Name
* Page:
** Name
** URL
** Section (application, loan, other)

We will also need to mask the following sensitive data fields from being recorded: [https://help.fullstory.com/hc/en-us/articles/4408633932439-Form-Privacy|https://help.fullstory.com/hc/en-us/articles/4408633932439-Form-Privacy|smart-link] 

* Password
* Owner social security number

* Change {{Please list everyone who owns 20% or more of the business.}} to {{Please list everyone who owns 20% or more or otherwise has significant control over the business.}}
* Add tooltip: {{Any owners that own 20% or more according to your cap table or articles of incorporation, as well as any individuals with significant responsibility to control, manage or direct the business, such as a Chief Executive Officer, Chief Financial Officer, Chief Operating Officer, President, or any other individual who regularly performs similar functions.}}

